snippet: Graeme McDowell finished with a 4-under-par 68 and won the World Challenge in Thousand Oaks, Calif., for his first title in two years.
abstract: Graeme McDowell wins World Challenge golf tournament in Thousand Oaks, Calif, his first title in two years.
